Package com.link_intersystems.jdbc.test.db.sakila

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SakilaDB
    The complete sakila sample database as provided by mysql.
    SakilaEmptyDatabaseFactory
    A ParameterResolver that provides a Connection to a H2 database initialized with the sakila sample database provided by mysql that only contains the film related tables: "actor", "film_actor", "film", "language", "film_category", "category".
    SakilaEmptyDB
    An empty version of the SakilaDB that contains no data, just the empty tables.
    SakilaH2DatabaseFactory  
    SakilaSlimDatabaseFactory
    A ParameterResolver that provides a Connection to a H2 in memory database initialized with the sakila sample database provided by mysql that only contains the film related tables: "actor", "film_actor", "film", "language", "film_category", "category".
    SakilaSlimDB
    A slim version of the SakilaDB that contains only data for: actor film_actor film language film_category category
    SakilaTinyDatabaseFactory
    A ParameterResolver that provides a Connection to a H2 in memory database initialized with the sakila sample database provided by mysql that only contains the film related tables: "actor", "film_actor", "film", "language", "film_category", "category".
    SakilaTinyDB
    A tiny version of the SakilaDB that contains only data for the actors with id 1 and 2.
